---
const team = [
  {
    name: 'Danielle Finch',
    role: 'Co-Founder & CEO',
    bio: '14 years scaling tech across 170 countries, including GE, Michelin, and HomeToGo.',
    fun: 'Also: despite being organized, manages to leave something behind at least once a trip.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Emmanuel Annor',
    role: 'Co-Founder & CTO',
    bio: 'MSc from Carnegie Mellon. Spent his career building AI features that digitize offline economies, from rural farmers to remote tourism operators.',
    fun: 'Also: sees himself as an artist, although his drawing skills strongly disagree.',
  },
  {
    name: 'Rogers Nasasira',
    role: 'Business Operations Lead',
    bio: '7 years leading travel operations in Uganda, formerly with the Travolution global CBTO network.',
    fun: "Also: the team's official Herdsman, having navigated potholes and elephants on the road.",
  },
  {
    name: 'Sabiiti Fenekansi',
    role: 'Training Manager',
    bio: 'Founder of Kitara Foundation for Regional Tourism, with 10 years developing sustainable tourism curriculum.',
    fun: 'Also: the team storyteller, always making connections wherever we go.',
  },
];
---

<section
  id="team"
  class="relative py-20 lg:py-32 bg-white overflow-hidden"
>
  <div class="absolute inset-0 overflow-hidden pointer-events-none">
    <div class="absolute top-1/4 right-0 w-96 h-96 bg-primary-100/20 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-1/4 left-0 w-80 h-80 bg-accent-blue/10 rounded-full blur-3xl"></div>
  </div>

  <div class="container mx-auto px-4 sm:px-6 lg:px-8 relative z-10">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto">
      <div class="text-center mb-16 lg:mb-20" data-animate>
        <h2 class="text-3xl sm:text-4xl lg:text-5xl font-bold text-brand-dark-purple mb-4">
          Meet the Team
        </h2>
        <div class="w-24 h-1 bg-gradient-to-r from-primary-500 to-primary-600 mx-auto rounded-full"></div>
      </div>

      <!-- Founder story (with founders photo) -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-2 gap-10 lg:gap-14 items-center mb-16 lg:mb-20" data-animate>
        <div class="order-2 lg:order-1">
          <div class="space-y-5 text-lg text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
            <p>
              In 2024, Co-Founder and CEO <strong class="text-brand-dark-purple">Danielle</strong> discovered community-based tourism in Malaysian Borneo. She had the time of her life and discovered an industry nobody was building for; she subsequently left her job at one of Europe's leading travel tech companies to fix it.
            </p>
            <p>
              One year later, she was on a bus in Rwanda and sat next to a fellow founder who told her about Norrsken House Kigali, one of Africa's leading innovation hubs. Norrsken is how she found Co-Founder and CTO <strong class="text-brand-dark-purple">Emmanuel</strong>.
            </p>
            <p>
              The two clicked from their very first meeting. Emmanuel has his master's from Carnegie Mellon and spent the first five years of his career building remote-first applications for 70,000+ farmers across Africa and Asia. Danielle spent 10 years in enterprise digitization for global brands before moving to HomeToGo, where she ran customer operations for half a million travelers a year and led teams that beat Airbnb, Booking.com, Vacasa and Vrbo for best customer experience in the industry.
            </p>
            <p>
              Our collective experience, remote-first tech for farmers with no connectivity and enterprise operations for half a million travelers a year, is exactly what lets us build for both ends of this problem. The same infrastructure that onboards a CBTO in the hills of Uganda also runs the operations for the world's biggest travel companies.
            </p>
          </div>
        </div>
        <div class="order-1 lg:order-2">
          <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl ring-1 ring-black/5">
            <img
              src="/images/equera-founders.webp"
              alt="Equera co-founders Danielle Finch and Emmanuel Annor"
              class="w-full aspect-[4/3] object-cover"
              loading="lazy"
            />
          </div>
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Team member cards -->
      <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 xl:grid-cols-4 gap-8 lg:gap-10 mb-16 lg:mb-20">
        {team.map((member) => (
          <div
            class="bg-white rounded-2xl p-6 lg:p-8 border border-gray-100 shadow-lg hover:shadow-xl hover:-translate-y-1 transition-all duration-300 flex flex-col"
            data-animate
          >
            <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-brand-dark-purple mb-1">
              {member.name}
            </h3>
            <p class="text-primary-500 font-semibold text-sm mb-4">
              {member.role}
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-700 text-sm lg:text-base leading-relaxed flex-1 mb-4">
              {member.bio}
            </p>
            <p class="text-gray-500 text-sm italic border-l-2 border-primary-200 pl-3">
              {member.fun}
            </p>
          </div>
        ))}
      </div>

      <!-- Team photo -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto mb-16 lg:mb-20" data-animate>
        <div class="relative rounded-2xl overflow-hidden shadow-xl ring-1 ring-black/5">
          <img
            src="/images/equera-team-table.webp"
            alt="The Equera team working together around a table"
            class="w-full h-auto object-cover"
            loading="lazy"
          />
        </div>
      </div>

      <!-- Mission closing -->
      <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto text-center" data-animate>
        <p class="text-lg lg:text-xl text-gray-700 leading-relaxed">
          We span inbound and outbound markets, tech and tourism, two continents. United by one mission: <strong class="text-brand-dark-purple">to restore equity in travel by building infrastructure that works for everyone, not just the 1%.</strong>
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>
